import { Component } from '@angular/core';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-login',
  templateUrl: './login.component.html',
  styleUrls: ['./login.component.scss']
})
export class LoginComponent {

}
<mat-card>
  <mat-toolbar  class="title">Login</mat-toolbar>
  <mat-card-content>
    <form  [formGroup]="form" class="min-width">
      <mat-form-field  class="full-width" appearance="fill">
        <input matInput placeholder="E-mail" formControlName="email">
      </mat-form-field>
      <mat-form-field class="full-width" appearance="fill">
        <input matInput placeholder="Senha" formControlName="senha">
      </mat-form-field>
    </form>
    <mat-card-actions >

      <button  class="acoes" mat-raised-button color="primary" (click)="onLogar()" >Entrar</button>
      <button  class="acoes" mat-raised-button  (click)="onCancel()" >Recuperar senha</button>
  </mat-card-actions>
  </mat-card-content>

</mat-card>
